                    <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                    <span>Consistent self-care routine that actually fits her real life</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                    <span>Has a plan for when things get hard again (because they will)</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
